import Vue from 'vue'
import Vuex from 'vuex'
import VuexPersistence from 'vuex-persist'

import user from './modules/user/index'
import spread from './modules/spread/index'
import webPage from './modules/webPage/index'
import marketing from './modules/marketing/index'
import library from './modules/library/index'
import circle from './modules/circle/index'
import system from './modules/system/index'
import dialog from './modules/dialog/index'
import articles from './modules/articles/index'
Vue.use(Vuex)
const vuexLocal = new VuexPersistence({
    storage: window.localStorage
})
const store = new Vuex.Store({
    modules: {
        user,
        spread,
        webPage,
        marketing,
        library,
        circle,
        system,
        dialog,
        articles
    },
    plugins: [
        vuexLocal.plugin
    ]
})

export default store
